data.description: Immaculate and well cared for 3 bedroom 2 bath home off Knollwood Drive in West Mobile. Brand new fortified, architectural shingle roof 2023. Note this open concept plan with family room with a cathedral ceiling, woodburning fireplace that also has gas logs, and new flooring. Kitchen has granite countertops, electric stove, and built-in microwave, pretty backsplash, and a separate eating area.  Split bedroom plan. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and its own private bathroom with granite countertops.  The other two bedrooms share a jack and Jill type bathroom with granite countertops that also opens to a small hallway. Bedrooms have new flooring in 2024. Super livable floor plan with very little wasted space. Outside has a separate storage room coming off the side of the house and a separate shed in the back with a window unit. Would make a great workshop. Deck overlooking a very private backyard. The outside trim was painted in 2023 and most of the inside was painted in 2024. Outside AC condenser=2023.  "Not AI comments, written by the listing agent. Lol." **Listing Broker makes no representation to accuracy of square footage. Buyer to verify. Any/All updates per seller(s).**
